citation: Justice and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2009 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Justice and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2009 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Justice and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2009 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
